<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>A 股连续下跌筛选（Baostock 本地数据）</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f1419;
      --panel: #1a2332;
      --text: #e7ecf3;
      --muted: #9aa7b2;
      --accent: #5b8cff;
      --border: #2a3545;
      --down: #ff6b6b;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.5;
    }
    header {
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #15202b 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
    }
    h1 { margin: 0 0 0.35rem; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 650; }
    .meta { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
    main { padding: 1rem 1.25rem 2.5rem; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.92rem; }
    th, td { padding: 0.55rem 0.5rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); vertical-align: top; }
    th { color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.78rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
    tr:hover td { background: rgba(91, 140, 255, 0.06); }
    .num { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; text-align: right; }
    .pct { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; text-align: right; }
    .neg { color: var(--down); }
    details.sub { margin: 0.35rem 0 0; }
    details.sub summary {
      cursor: pointer; color: var(--accent); font-size: 0.85rem; user-select: none;
    }
    .inner { margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem; padding: 0.5rem 0.65rem; background: var(--panel); border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .inner table { font-size: 0.82rem; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.75rem; background: #2f3b4d; color: var(--muted); }
    footer { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.82rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .empty { color: var(--muted); padding: 2rem 0; text-align: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>连续下跌 ≥ {{ min_streak_days }} 天（截至最新本地数据）</h1>
    <div class="meta">
      生成时间：{{ generated_at }} · 配置的数据结束日：{{ data_end_date or "—" }} ·
      近一月口径：{{ lookback_trading_days }} 个交易日涨跌幅
    </div>
  </header>
  <main>
    {% if rows|length == 0 %}
      <p class="empty">暂无符合条件的股票，或尚未运行同步脚本生成 <code>data/</code>。</p>
    {% else %}
      <table aria-label="连续下跌股票">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>股票名称</th>
            <th>代码</th>
            <th>ST 标记</th>
            <th class="num">最新收盘</th>
            <th class="num">连跌天数</th>
            <th class="pct">连跌总跌幅</th>
            <th class="pct">近{{ lookback_trading_days }}日跌幅</th>
            <th>明细</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {% for r in rows %}
          <tr>
            <td>{{ r.stock_name }}</td>
            <td><span class="badge">{{ r.code }}</span></td>
            <td>{{ r.is_st }}</td>
            <td class="num">{{ "%.3f"|format(r.latest_close) }}</td>
            <td class="num">{{ r.streak_days }}</td>
            <td class="pct neg">{{ "%.2f"|format(r.streak_total_pct) }}%</td>
            <td class="pct {% if r.month_20_pct is not none and r.month_20_pct < 0 %}neg{% endif %}">
              {% if r.month_20_pct is not none %}
                {{ "%.2f"|format(r.month_20_pct) }}%
              {% else %}
                —
              {% endif %}
            </td>
            <td>
              <details class="sub">
                <summary>展开每日跌幅</summary>
                <div class="inner">
                  <table>
                    <thead>
                      <tr>
                        <th>日期</th>
                        <th class="num">收盘</th>
                        <th class="pct">当日涨跌幅</th>
                      </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                      {% for d in r.details %}
                      <tr>
                        <td>{{ d.date }}</td>
                        <td class="num">{{ "%.3f"|format(d.close) }}</td>
                        <td class="pct {% if d.day_pct < 0 %}neg{% endif %}">{{ "%.2f"|format(d.day_pct) }}%</td>
                      </tr>
                      {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                </div>
              </details>
            </td>
          </tr>
          {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    {% endif %}
  </main>
  <footer>
    数据来源于 Baostock；ST 标记为基于证券简称的启发式规则，非交易所官方字段。仅供学习研究，不构成投资建议。
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
